        <div id="mainGameContainer"  class="baseFlex flexCol absoluteParent">
            <div id="helpContainer" class="helpContainer scrollable hidden">
                <p>For an individual game of <strong>Wordle</strong>, a "common" five-letter word is chosen, and you have to guess it by the time you exceed the given maximum guess limit.</p>
                <p>Your guesses must be valid words; no just entering random characters for one of the guesses.</p>
                <p>To actually submit a guess, you can type either by using an actual keyboard, or by clicking on the keys on the virtual keyboard on the page.</p>
                <p>Use the 'Enter/Return' key to submit your guess, and the backspace key to delete a letter if you make a mistake.</p>
                <p>To make the process possible, your incorrect guesses will provide details about whether the characters in your guesses are present in the actual answer.</p>
                <div class="sampleRow baseFlex flexRow">
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex absent"><span>R</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex absent"><span>I</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex wrongLocation"><span>S</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex absent"><span>E</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex absent"><span>N</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="sampleRow baseFlex flexRow">
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex wrongLocation"><span>S</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex wrongLocation"><span>T</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex exactMatch"><span>A</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex wrongLocation"><span>L</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex absent"><span>L</span></div>
                </div>
                <div class="sampleRow baseFlex flexRow">
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex exactMatch"><span>B</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex exactMatch"><span>L</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex exactMatch"><span>A</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex exactMatch"><span>S</span></div>
                    <div class="tileContainer small baseFlex exactMatch"><span>T</span></div>
                </div>
                <p>All letters except the 'S' in the first guess above are not present in the actual answer. The 'S' is present, but not in the same location.</p>
                <p>The second guess shows the 'S', 'T', and first 'L' are present in the correct answer, but again, not in the same location. The 'A', however, is exactly where it will be in the answer.</p>
                <p>In addition, the second guess shows that there is only one 'L' in the answer, as the second is shown as absent. The 'S' and 'T' however, are just known be present AT LEAST once.</p>
                <p>The third guess shows that the <strong>Wordle</strong> round has been successfully solved.</p>
                <p>Enabling <strong>Hard Mode</strong> requires that all future guesses utilize all letters whose exact position are known.</p>
            </div>
